<br>
I was wondering how much religion affects a chanter (planning on a inny worshipping de chanter)?  ie will I be kos on the isle in oot even if I manage to get an alliance spell (or whatever it's called) off on a npc b4 going to buy the kiola nuts? and will I be kos in oggok or the inn in freeport?<br>
<br>
how much affect does religion really have regarding faction?<br>
<br>
<br>
